{
  "stem": "3973.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "At that time, if you reported a Jew, you would get 5 kilos of sugar which was quite a reward.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So I was waiting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Then I said, well, I have to allow so much time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "This was-- the potato fields were pretty high.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I was going to find my way and hide in the potato fields for the night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And just then, the-- a German truck stopped.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "In his view, he was coming over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I waved to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And-- and I gave him the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I went to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "There were many, many adventures.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I mean, getting to Krakow, the-- the-- the access to Krakow was always blocked on the main streets, primarily because people coming from the villages usually were black marketeers who were bringing food and stuff into town.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "So they inspected everybody and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I mean, I had ways of getting through.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I mean, I was perfect at that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Anyway, I went in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had no place to stay.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I had some people, some Poles I knew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "But they wouldn't take me in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I would sleep in-- like, in the house where we lived in way on the top there is a floor which leads to the attic where people used to hang their laundry.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I would sleep on top of there or find places, where courtyards, boxes, crates, whatever there was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And during the day, I would read books and go to the movies.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Total-- I mean, this was a way of-- totally unreasonable.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was thinking only of the immediate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember sometimes go to-- went to the movies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By the time I came out, I didn't know where I was going to go to sleep.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
